				<td colspan="2"><span>Wow, i had exactly the same experience in my first hard ldon. To many resists on paci, hard to keep 3 mobs messed, tanks going down etc.
<br />

<br />
first thing i did for myself was get me a tradeskill jewel: + 50 cha and augmented it with another +6 cha.
<br />
then i bought me the stein for an additional 25 Cha. and of course augmented it:)
<br />

<br />
now this close to an hundred extra cha, + our cha song brings me close to 300 cha in total. I hardly get a critical fail on blue mobs anymore. So i now paci blues, and pull whites.
<br />
This way i never have more then 2 - 3 mobs on a pull.
<br />
Next thing i did was JF 1. now i hardly get resists on mess either, and pulling/cc-ing hards has become mannageable w/o getting a headache:)
<br />

<br />

<br />
Now i am so far that i prefer mess pulling. Mostly i lul one in a chain, mess another, have three mobs incoming, mess one more, run to camp and fade.
<br />
Makes it a lot less a hassle, and even more fun:)
<br />

<br />
hope that helps a bit,
